</Dialog>
```

**Alert Dialog** — `import { AlertDialog, AlertDialogContent, AlertDialogHeader, AlertDialogTitle, AlertDialogDescription, AlertDialogFooter, AlertDialogAction, AlertDialogCancel } from "@/components/ui/alert-dialog"`
```tsx
